  "body": "# Add markdown rendering in the composer\r\n\r\n| As a user\r\n\r\n| I want to see the markdown rendered in the composer\r\n\r\n| So I know how it will look like when posted\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nWhen typing some markdown in the composer, the text should reflect how it will look like when posted.\r\n\r\nCurrently supported markdown is:\r\n\r\n**bold**\r\n\r\n*italic*\r\n\r\n~strike-through~ (to be checked)\r\n\r\n`code`\r\n\r\n```jsx\r\ncode block\r\n```\r\n\r\n| quote\r\n\r\n### Designs\r\n\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/wA8Epdki2OWa8Vr067PCNQ/Composer-for-Mobile?node-id=2630%3A207636",
